Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:11470,13222}{\i1}I want to be pretty…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:14223,19186}{\i1}I want to wear nice clothes\Nand be more beautiful than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:19186,24483}{\i1}If I do, he'll turn around and look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:24483,27903}{\i1}He'll turn around, because I'm pretty.
