Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:45045,45921}{\i1}Doi-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:53095,54346}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:54805,56807}Oh, Mayumi! You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:59518,61144}Oh, you look so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:61144,63230}You look really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:63939,68151}My dad just came back and brought\Nlots of western clothes with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:68151,71280}Must be nice,\Nhaving a father like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:71280,74199}He brought accessories\Nwith him too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:74700,76576}That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:76576,78120}It's nothing special, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:78120,81415}When he comes back,\Nhe never stops talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:81415,83166}What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:83166,84626}I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:84626,89214}I guess you're right…\NI should be happy that he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89214,91383}He got back in time\Nfor my birthday, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91383,93427}So, you're coming\Nto my party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93427,95053}– Yeah!\N– Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95053,96346}You're coming too, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96346,99182}Oh? Ah, yes…\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99182,101226}Are there boys coming, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101226,104563}There are. Doi-kun already said\Nthat he's coming, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104563,107399}Mayumi!\NYou're going out with Doi-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107399,108358}Of course not…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108358,110319}No way!\NYou're going out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110319,112321}No, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112321,114072}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114865,116616}I said that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117367,122831}We just talk at school all the time\Nand he's helped me a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132007,134551}What? You've cleaned\Nthe blackboard for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134968,138388}I completely forgot.\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139431,141767}{\i1}He has such a kind voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141767,145729}{\i1}After that, I became\Ncurious about Doi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145729,150275}{\i1}Whenever I looked at him,\Nhe was already looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151360,153278}{\i1}Was that just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156490,159117}{\i1}I have nothing to wear…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164539,165832}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173340,174925}Oh, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179304,180847}It's so pretty…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180847,185477}You can't wear it.\NWe don't even know who it's from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185477,188397}It might have been delivered\Nto the wrong house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188772,193568}Besides, I can't really explain it, but that\None piece makes me really uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217968,219052}It fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219803,224015}It's almost like it was made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234151,235610}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235610,240282}Hey, Mom, is it okay for me to wear that\Nto Mayumi-chan's birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240282,241199}No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242075,246997}Why? Do you want them all to laugh at me\Nfor wearing my own weird clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246997,249082}You've already got lots of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249082,250834}You just bought some more\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250834,254171}That's not fair! Please, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254504,258675}You're just going to your friends' house.\NWhy do you need to get all dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258675,260135}Stop being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263972,267559}{\i1}It's not like I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267934,268810}Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268810,269728}{\i1}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269728,270520}Hashimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271772,272772}Doi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273273,277277}Hey, you're going to\Nthe party today too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277277,278487}Y-Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278487,281865}What a relief! I was invited, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281865,285202}This will be the first time\NI see you in your own clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285202,287913}Well… I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289039,290874}{\i1}I don't want to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291291,292834}{\i1}I don't want to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293376,296296}I don't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298757,302761}It would've been nice\Nif I could go wearing that one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304137,305388}Wh-What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309935,314397}Gosh, why can't Mom\Nremember to close it properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320695,324282}It's Mom's fault…\NIt's all her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324282,326284}All hers…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328161,329704}Yuuko sure is late, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329704,332374}She even said she was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344928,346137}Hashimoto…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348640,352769}Hey, Doi-kun,\Nlet's go and play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352769,355438}It's my birthday today, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355438,356022}Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357732,359609}Yeah, okay.\NWe'll bring Hashimoto, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363613,366741}{\i1}Only I have to die…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371121,372664}{\i1}Only me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374958,377460}{\i1}Only I have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379379,380380}Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380714,381965}{\i1}Doi-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382215,383049}Doi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383049,384259}Doi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384259,385886}{\i1}Doi-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387888,390849}{\i1}Doi-kun…\NLook at me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403153,408867}{\i1}I was discharged a few days later and found out\Nthat Doi-kun had transferred schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408867,414122}{\i1}After talking to other boys,\NI learned that he liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414122,418376}{\i1}If I hadn't worn that dress,\Nthat would never have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418376,423256}{\i1}But, I can't afford\Nto feel any regrets now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423256,426718}{\i1}That's because\Nafter yesterday's dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426718,431222}{\i1}I felt deep inside that the one piece\Nthat should've disappeared was back in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432682,436269}{\i1}I haven't checked yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436269,438229}{\i1}I'm too scared to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438229,446446}{\i1}I'm so scared of that eerie one piece,\Nthat every day is filled with fear.
